<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="et">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kalender - Avaleht</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #e9f4fc;
            color: #444;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                color: #0077b6;
            }

        /* Navigation Links */
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

            .nav-links a {
                color: #0077b6;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: 500;
                padding: 8px 12px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
            }

                .nav-links a:hover {
                    background-color: #caf0f8;
                }

        /* Container Styles */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

            .container h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                color: #0096c7;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .container p {
                color: #555;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        /* Button Styles */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #0077b6;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background-color: #34a853;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background-color: #023e8a;
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            background-color: #2a7a3b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Kalender</h1>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="/Home/Index">Avaleht</a>
            <a href="/Event/Index">Kalender</a>
            <a href="/Account/Login">Logi sisse</a>
            <a href="/Account/Register">Registreeru</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Tere tulemast Kalendrisse!</h2>
        <p>Lihtsusta oma päeva juhtimist ja hallake sündmusi mugavalt.</p>

        <div>
            <a href="/Event/Index" class="btn">Vaata kalendrit</a>
            <a href="/Event/Create" class="btn btn-success">Lisa sündmus</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
